variables.name: prompt-assignment
variables.description: A variable you can use for assignments

defaultValue.string:
Please complete the following information on form LE-10:

1.       Account No.  Enter your Illinois unemployment account number

2.       Employer  Enter your businesss legal name

3.       Located At  Enter your businesss street address, city, state, and zip code

4.       Telephone Number  Enter your businesss telephone number

5.       Email Address  Enter your companys contact email address         

6.       Signature  Have the person noted under Name of Employer sign the form

7.       Name of Employer  Enter your businesss legal name

8.       By  Enter persons name signing the form, should be an officer of the company

9.       Title  Enter the title of the person signing the form

10.     Date  Enter the date the form is signed

Thank you
